description: [Premium Times] The Super Eagles have always found heroes at AFCON tournaments and they are looking for another after the likes of Odegbami, Amuneke, and Mba.
title: Africa: Golden Moments - Three Legendary Nigerian Players in Afcon Finals

description: [CAF] Abidjan -- South Africa claimed the TotalEnergies CAF Africa Cup of Nations third place play-off on Saturday, beating DR Congo 6-5 on penalties after a goalless 120 minutes.
title: Africa: South Africa Secure TotalEnergies CAF AFCON Bronze After Shootout
